'''People's Liberation Army of Turkey-Revolutionary Path of Turkey''' ({{lang-tr|Türkiye Halk Kurtulus Ordusu-Türkiye Devriminin Yolu}}) was a [[splinter group]] of the [[People's Liberation Army of Turkey]] (THKO). THKO-TDY appeared in 1975.

